      "side": 1,
      "message": "Is all OEM data going to be a simple key-value or is it intended to be JSON structured?  How do we expect bmcweb to transpose that and how to we intend them to be able to match it up with a schema?\n\nWhat if two different parties want to add their own OEM data for a single event?  ie. a chip vendor like AMD and a system vendor like Quanta (or Meta)?",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 14,
        "startChar": 25,
        "endLine": 14,
        "endChar": 32
      },
      "revId": "67fcea985d17403d9414fcf637f462fb6cb4bce0",
